Entry-Name: .description
Content-Type: text/plain

1. Open file script
2. Select line and choose "Source\Comment" from context menu
3. Select several lines and choose "Source\Add Block Comments" from context menu
4. Make sure that lines are commented
5. Choose "Source\Remove Block Comments" from context menu
6. Make sure that lines are uncommented

Bug:
When first line of block is commented, then several lines are commented incorrectly
